title: Dreo oscillating fan for bedroom,150°+120° Omni-Directional Quiet Floor Fans with Smart Control, 110ft Pedestal Fan with DC Motor, 9 Speeds, 6 Modes, 43'' Inches, 12H Timer, Wi-Fi/Voice/Alexa
breadCrumbs: Home & Kitchen › Heating, Cooling & Air Quality › Household Fans › Pedestal Fans
features: 𝙐𝙡𝙩𝙞𝙢𝙖𝙩𝙚 𝙈𝙪𝙡𝙩𝙞𝙛𝙪𝙣𝙘𝙩𝙞𝙤𝙣𝙖𝙡 𝙎𝙢𝙖𝙧𝙩 𝙁𝙖𝙣: DREO PolyFan integrates strong points of floor-standing, air circulation and smart control into one. This fan for bedroom features 9 wind speeds and 6 wind types, from turbo blasts to soothing sleep winds, it adapts to your every mood, need, and environment you want to use it on.

𝙁𝙖𝙧-𝙧𝙚𝙖𝙘𝙝𝙞𝙣𝙜 𝙖𝙣𝙙 𝙎𝙩𝙖𝙗𝙡𝙚 𝘼𝙞𝙧𝙛𝙡𝙤𝙬: Using TurboSilent technology and DC motor, this floor fan with remote increases its wind volume higher by 66%. The air circulator fan reaches a staggering 110 ft range to cover every inch of room, and effectively promoting the air circulation.

𝙊𝙢𝙣𝙞-𝙙𝙞𝙧𝙚𝙘𝙩𝙞𝙤𝙣𝙖𝙡 𝙊𝙨𝙘𝙞𝙡𝙡𝙖𝙩𝙞𝙤𝙣: Unlike most fans, this oscillating fan bringing simultaneous 150˚ horizontal and 120˚ vertical oscillation and an adjustable pedestal of 37.5-43 inches for more flexibility. Customize it to any angle and direction on the DREO app as you like and bring comfort to each space of room.

𝙏𝙝𝙚 𝙎𝙢𝙖𝙧𝙩 𝘼𝙨𝙨𝙞𝙨𝙩𝙖𝙣𝙘𝙚 𝙤𝙛 𝘾𝙤𝙤𝙡𝙞𝙣𝙜 𝙇𝙞𝙛𝙚: Enjoy smart and convenient with the DREO app. Customize any mode, speed and angle as you like, arrange schedules according to your daily routines, edit temperature block to match different wind strength. Try to use touch panel, handy remote control, app and voice to feel this pedestal fan.

𝙀𝙭𝙥𝙚𝙧𝙞𝙚𝙣𝙘𝙚 𝙒𝙞𝙣𝙙 𝙬𝙞𝙩𝙝 𝙉𝙤 𝙎𝙤𝙪𝙣𝙙: Using a Brushless DC motor and bionic blade design, the efficiency of the standing fan increased by 40% and can blow air down to an unhearable 25dB. The sound of his quiet fan is less than a whisper.

𝘿𝙍𝙀𝙊 𝙈𝙖𝙠𝙚𝙨 𝘾𝙤𝙢𝙛𝙤𝙧𝙩 𝙀𝙖𝙨𝙞𝙚𝙧: Don't worry about turning on your room fan when falling sleep for it has built-in 12H timer. Blades and grille can be easily dettached for cleaning to keep your air always fresh. Sturdy metal connecting neck and stable base make this floor fan more durable.

title: Lasko X-Blower 6 Position High Velocity Pivoting Utility Blower Fan for Cooling, Ventilating, Exhausting and Drying, 3 Speeds, AC Outlet, Circuit Breaker with Reset, USB Port, 11x9x12, Blue, X12905
breadCrumbs: Home & Kitchen › Heating, Cooling & Air Quality › Household Fans
description: With its rugged construction and stable design, the X-Blower Multi-Position Utility Blower Fan from Lasko is perfect for use in your garage, workshop, basement, kitchen, and more. Choose from 6 positions to direct the high-velocity air stream where you need it most for cooling, ventilating, exhausting, and drying. Choose from 3 powerful speeds with easy-to-use electronic controls. Comes equipped with a circuit breaker with reset button and a 3-prong grounded plug. Charge your mobile devices while you work with 2 convenient USB ports. Plus, a built-in 120-volt outlet allows you to plug in additional fans, etc. so you can get work accomplished quickly and easily. Move this utility fan from place-to-place with the easy-grip handle. Comes fully assembled.
features: ✅【HIGH VELOCITY AIR STREAM】Powered by 3 fan speeds and a CFM of 370 on high, this heavy-duty air mover is best for helping the hottest spaces in the house to feel cooler, circulating and exhausting stuffy air, and drying out wet carpeting and floors.

✅【COMPACT AND ADAPTABLE】This lightweight blower fan is a breeze to move from room-to-room or job-to-job, and you can use its 6-position capability to direct the air flow where it’s needed most; Ideal for job sites, basements, garages and all areas of the home
✅【CONVENIENT FFEATURES】This versitile blower fan from Lasko features a built-in 120V accessory outlet and 2 USB ports to power additional devices
✅【BUILT IN SAFETY】This blower floor fan is ETL Listed and comes with a circuit breaker with reset button, and a 3-prong grounded plug, making it a safe choice for a cooling breeze
✅【SPACE SAVING DESIGN】Standing only 11 in. tall with a small 9 in. x 12 in. footprint, this small-but-mighty fan needs minimal floor space—easily fitting in places where pedestal & box fans won’t.

Groundbreaking beyond any floor fan: While most fans limit your options to a couple of speeds, Dreo PolyFan 513S brings more ways to control air with 6 wind modes and up to 8 speeds, whether you want close-range cooling or blow a powerful jet of air throughout your living room, this standing fan gets you covered.

Omni-directional Oscillation: Experience unparalleled air circulation with this standing fan. Its 120° horizontal and 105° vertical oscillation distributes air more efficiently throughout your entire room, allowing you to share the freshness not only you alone but also with your family and friends. You can even customize the airflow direction easily from your smartphone. It will also automatically reset to its initial state after being turned off, if it has been oscillating during use.

Ready for true intelligent control? With Dreo Smart Fan, you can effortlessly switch modes, adjust oscillation angles and speeds using just your voice, smartphone, or convenient remote control. The built-in display allows you to quickly check the status of your device. If you prefer manual settings, PolyFan 513S got those too.

Tilt-back fan head 
Create the comfort you desire with the tilt-back fan head feature on Lasko pedestal fans. Pivot the fan head towards the ceiling or floor to circulate air efficiently throughout your space and boost the effectiveness of air conditioning in the summer and heat (from fireplace or central heating system) in the winter. 
Widespread oscillation 
A key feature on Lasko pedestal fans, widespread oscillation quickly provides cooling airflow and comfort throughout the room. Easily turn the 90 degree oscillation on or off with a switch at the rear of the fan or with the press of a button on remote oscillation fan models. Use the stand fan oscillation mode to boost the effects of air conditioning and efficiently move cool air throughout your space. 
Electronic controls 
Front facing electronic controls feature 3 speed fan settings and up to 4-hour timer. Plus, conveniently operate the fan from the comfort of your bed or seat with the multi-function remote control. 
Perfect for Any Space 
Lasko, Since 1906 
THE BLUE PLUG is an important safety feature on all Lasko residential pedestal fans. The plug is designed to cut off electric current to the fan if it detects a potentially hazardous electrical fault in the fan’s motor or power supply. 
Great Fan for the Kitchen 
The kitchen can be one of the warmest spots in the home. Feel cooler and more comfortable while cooking, cleaning, or spending time with family and friends, using a pedestal fan to circulate the air. The widespread oscillation feature quickly and quietly moves cooling airflow throughout the room. Lasko stand fans feature tilt-back heads and adjustable height to allow you to customize the airflow and maximize comfort in your kitchen. 
Great Fan for the Bedroom 
If your bedroom feels too warm or stuffy, a pedestal fan is an excellent choice to help you feel cooler. Adjust the height of your Lasko pedestal fan, also known as a stand fan, to direct the airflow to blow across your bed, keeping you cooler while you sleep. Bring cooler air in from the outside by placing your fan by the window or aim it out the window to exhaust the stuffy air. With a Lasko pedestal fan, you can make your bedroom a comfortable oasis for relaxation and rest.

features: SCREW-IN DESIGN: Our socket fan light adopts the E26 screw-in base, so there is no need to spend a lot time and money to install the fan. You can install the fan by yourself. title: fan-dam® Ceiling Fan Blade Spoiler for Increased Airflow - Six Pack
breadCrumbs: Tools & Home Improvement › Lighting & Ceiling Fans › Ceiling Fans & Accessories › Ceiling Fans
description: More Breeze, Less SpeedBy attaching fan-dam flaps to your existing ceiling fan blades, saving money and improving airflow is a breeze. fan-dam is the only product of its kind—a unique air-dam ceiling fan blade spoiler that easily affixes to existing ceiling fan blades to create more air flow at lower speeds. Inexpensive, discreet, and easy-to-install, fan-dam saves energy and money while keeping you cooler in summer and warmer in winter.Safe and Easy No Tools Required Improved Air Flow at Lower Fan Speeds U.S. Patent Stay Cool-Less Fuel Made in the USAWhat is fan-dam?fan-dam is a patented, adhesive-bonded, flexible air-dam ceiling fan blade spoiler that attaches to flat paddle-style fan blades to improve downdraft airflow when cooling and better updraft in heating (reverse) mode. fan-dam flaps produce more efficient airflow and comfortably save energy and money.How Does fan-dam Work?In cooling mode, fan-dam functions as a spoiler, increasing the volume of cooling down-wash breeze. In heating mode, fan-dam functions as an air-dam, improving warm air re-circulation throughout the room. Its unique, patented design increases safety and reduces inefficient drag at higher blade speeds.What’s the Technology Behind fan-dam?fan-dam is a U.S. patented, high density, transparent dual-durometer extruded vinyl aerodynamic ceiling fan blade attachment. It is easily attached to the trailing edge of a traditional flat fan blade with clear peel-and-stick high-bond acrylic adhesive. The result is increased air flow from traditional flat ceiling fan blades at all fan speeds.

TroubleshootingIf the fan suddenly starts to oscillate,If the fan suddenly starts to oscillate,It is normal when the fan is in Advanced Sleep Mode. It will automatically start oscillating after one hour of operation, which is its default setting. If the air output has decreased after cleaning the wind wheel,If the air output has decreased after cleaning the wind wheel,Please make sure that the screws are aligned with the flat surface of the motor shaft during installation, not the arc surface, otherwise the air output will be reduced!If the fan suddenly stops,If the fan suddenly stops,It could be a timer accidentally set before. title: Fans First: Change The Game, Break the Rules & Create an Unforgettable Experience
author: Jesse Cole
breadCrumbs: Kindle Store › Kindle eBooks › Business & Money
bookDescription:
The Savannah Bananas should not exist.
You can't name any of their players. They play in a 1920s-era ballpark with no ads or billboards. They play in kilts, stilts, and stilettos. They even have an all-grandma dance team: the Banana Nanas.
Everything the Bananas do is unconventional. It shouldn’t work.
And yet they sell out every game, have a waitlist in the thousands, ship merchandise around the globe, and entertain millions of followers on social media.
ESPN calls the Bananas “the greatest show in baseball.”
How is this even possible?
Two words: Fans First.
Packed with behind-the-peel stories, hard-earned lessons, and a few other surprises, Fans First teaches you how to stand out in your marketplace, drive explosive growth, and inspire fanatical loyalty.
If this all sounds bananas, that’s the point. Normal leaders read normal books and get normal results. But if you’re ready to change the game, break the rules, and create your own unforgettable team, then it’s time to go Fans First.

aiReviewsSummary.text: Customers find the book readable and practical. They find it inspiring and engaging, with useful ideas for business improvements. The book makes them think about the fan experience and creative ways to improve it. Readers appreciate the excellent stories and real-life examples of determination and perseverance.

aPlusContent.title: Product Description
aPlusContent.rawText:
Product Description
Specifically designed for pressure demanding applications such as CPU or radiator cooling, the classic NF-P12 is a long-standing favourite among enthusiast users around the world and helped to found Noctua’s reputation as a top-tier manufacturer of premium quality quiet cooling components. The new redux edition reissues this award-winning model in a streamlined, accessibly priced package that has been reduced to the essential core: the NF-P12 premium fan. Its industry grade SSO bearing and over 150.000 hours MTTF rating make the NF-P12 redux a proven premium choice that provides trusted Noctua quality. The performance-oriented top speed of the 1700rpm PWM version is ideal for high efficiency case, radiator and CPU cooling as well as other applications that require both extended performance headroom and PWM for automatic speed control. 
Proven NF-P12 design 
Tens of thousands of quiet cooling enthusiasts around the globe swear by Noctua's classic NF-P12. Thanks to its impressive quietness, excellent performance and impeccable quality, the NF-P12 has become an established reference for quiet 120mm fans. 
Pressure-optimised Nine-Blade Design 
Specifically developed for high-impedance applications such as CPU coolers, water-cooling radiators or cases with tight fan grills, the NF-P12's nine-blade impeller provides outstanding pressure and airflow performance. 
SSO-Bearing 
Combining the proven concept of hydrodynamic bearing with an additional magnet that supports the self-stabilisation of the rotor axis, Noctua's time-tested technology has become synonymous with supremely quiet operation and exceptional long-term stability. 
Vortex-Control Notches 
Noctua's signature Vortex-Control Notches split up trailing edge vortices and thus spread the fan's noise emission over a wider range of frequencies. This measure makes the fan sound more pleasant to the human ear. 
Colour-customisable with NA-SAVP1 anti-vibration pads 
The fan’s frame can be outfitted with Noctua’s chromax line NA-SAVP1 anti-vibration pads. Available in black, red, blue, white, green and yellow, these pads not only damp minute vibrations but also allow the fan to be colour-customised in order to coordinate it with popular build colour schemes! 
Streamlined Redux Edition 
The redux product line reissues some of Noctua's most popular, award-winning models by presenting them in streamlined, accessibly priced packages. All redux edition products are industry proven, time-tested models that helped to found Noctua's reputation as a first-tier supplier of premium grade low noise cooling equipment.

1 Cooling and Charging 2 Easy to Store 3 Powerful But Quiet 4 Multi-purpose 
Easy to Carry 

Our Fans Said: The fan housing measures approximately 6.6”L x 5.6”W x 1.5”D when folded. It takes up very little space, and it is a good size to bring around because of its size and sleek design. 
Easy To Clean 

Our Fans Said: There is a front cover over the blades that may be removed by twisting the cover a few degrees. If you need to clean your fan blades on a regular basis to make it look cleaner, then it meets your needs! 
As an Emergency Power Source 

Our Fans Said: A very clever feature of this fan is its ability to operate as a power bank able to deliver its internal battery power to other devices via the USB-A output on the rear of the fan. It’s an unusual design feature not often found on these kinds of devices. It can even provide power to other devices while charging itself (‘daisy chain’ fashion), so if you find yourself with only one available USB outlet this can still halp. 
Foldable, Adjustable Stand 

Our Fans Said: It has a stand that allows it to be angled in the desired direction. The angle is adjustable simply by adjusting the back part, which can double as a handle to make it easy to carry, and it folds completely flat making it very easy to store when not in use. 
LEDs for Battery Life Display 

Our Fans Said: There is a nice led battery indicator on the front, and LEDs indicating the amount of charge left.

description: Product DescriptionFull-Function Remote Control Offering three fan speeds, this Comfort Zone adjustable height 18" oscillating pedestal fan with remote control can transition from generating a gentle breeze to powerful air flow with the push of a button. The remote control lets you adjust the fan speed and settings from a distance, or you can simply use the fan's front control panel. Oscillating Design for Increased Air Circulation This quiet table fan is equipped with an oscillating fan head that sways from side to side to create a gentle breeze throughout the entire room. The oscillating feature is ideal for living rooms, family movie nights and other group settings, or for creating consistent air flow in a smaller room. Quiet Motor for Minimal Sound A great option for those who need a fan to sleep, this quiet fan for bedrooms creates very little noise, even on the high-speed function. It provides a gentle, steady breeze while producing minimal sound, which can help provide relief on hot nights without interrupting your sleep cycle. Adjustable Tilt This 3-speed oscillating pedestal fan features an adjustable tilt that can be angled up or down to direct air flow where you need it. This helps to provide consistent relief from the heat on hot summer days, and it also serves as a suitable sleeping fan for those who need consistent air flow on their face or body.From the ManufacturerComfort Zone 18-Inch Deluxe oscillating pedestal fan with 3 speeds and timer setting. features: ADJUSTABLE SPEED OPTIONS: Experience customizable airflow with this oscillating pedestal fan that comes equipped with three-speed settings. Whether you prefer a gentle breeze to create a soothing atmosphere, medium speed for optimal comfort, or high speed for maximum air circulation, this fan allows you to easily select the desired speed to match your environment. Enjoy the flexibility and control provided by the multiple speed options, ensuring that the fan delivers the perfect level of cooling for any setting.

REMOTE CONTROL: Take full control of the fan's settings without leaving your seat. This pedestal fan comes with an intuitive and easy-to-use remote control that allows you to adjust its settings from anywhere in the room. With just a press of a button, you can conveniently switch the fan on or off, adjust the speed, set the timer, and even activate the oscillation feature. If you prefer direct control, the fan's front control panel provides a user-friendly interface for programming and adjusting the settings according to your preference.

TIMER FUNCTION: Take control of your cooling experience with the built-in timer feature of this pedestal fan. With the ability to set a desired duration, you can enjoy a refreshing breeze without worrying about leaving the fan running for extended periods. Simply program the fan to automatically shut off after a set time, ensuring energy efficiency and preventing unnecessary operation. Whether you want to cool down before bed or need a burst of fresh air during the day, the timer function allows you to customize your fan's operation.

AIRFLOW CONTROL: Experience precise control over the direction of cool air with the adjustable tilt and oscillating features of this indoor fan. Customize the airflow to suit your needs by adjusting the fan's tilt angle, allowing you to direct the breeze precisely where you desire it. The oscillating function enhances the distribution of cool air throughout the room, ensuring a comfortable and well-ventilated area. Whether you're working, relaxing, or sleeping, this fan provides the flexibility to create a personalized cooling experience.

WHISPER-QUIET OPERATION: Experience serene tranquility with this quiet bedroom fan featuring an almost silent motor. Designed to provide a peaceful environment, this fan ensures minimal noise disturbance, making it perfect for home offices and bedrooms where tranquility is essential. Enjoy a peaceful night's sleep or focus on your work without the distraction of loud fan noise. The quiet motor delivers efficient airflow while maintaining a peaceful ambiance, allowing you to stay cool and comfortable without sacrificing tranquility.

aPlusContent.title: Product Description
aPlusContent.rawText:
Product Description
52 Inch Low Profile Smart Ceiling Fan with Light 
This Striver 52 inch ceiling fan with light is perfect for modern, luxury, vintage, and stylish home decor. The flush mount design fits any low profile flat ceiling, install indoors or outdoors to enjoy nice air with this rustic ceiling fan.
For a variety of use, you can control this bedroom ceiling fan with a specialized handy remote, Carro Home App, Alexa, Google Assistant, and Siri Shortcuts. Works with voice control to satisfy your need on any occasion.
We engage in designs, and deliver the smart ceiling fan with proven quality to you. Elevate your living space with the ceiling fan, adding a clean and current look to your home.
Outstanding Quality and Superior Design 
The matte black fan blades are made of sturdy and lightweight ABS, let the high-performance ceiling fan delivers strong airflow easily. 
The motor housing with the black and gold finish design is luxurious and simple, allows the precision-balanced ceiling fan perfectly integrate in outdoor and indoor. 
The oval glass lampshade softens the overall design of the customized ceiling fan and enhances texture. 
Flush mount ceiling fan is suitable for low profile, easy to install. CANNOT be angled. 
This black ceiling fan with light is ETL-certified and safe for indoor and outdoor with step-by-step installation. (please do not pour water into the fan directly) 
3 Ways to Control Smart Ceiling Fan with Light 
Advanced Smart Control: Carro Home App 
This ceiling fan with light can be controlled using the Carro Home App (compatible for Android and IOS devices). Easily adjust the fan speed, dim the LED lights, alternate between color temperatures, set timers, create schedules, reverse the fan direction, and change fan modes.
When connecting to the app for the first time, make sure to turn off the Bluetooth and use only the 2.4Ghz network.
Voice Control: Smart Home Tech 
This smart ceiling fan integrates seamlessly with Alexa, Google Assistant, and Siri Shortcuts for hands-free access to your fan settings. Using a simple voice command you can control your fan speed, turn the light on/off, and even dim the brightness. Voice control is perfect in areas like your living room or kitchen where you often find yourself with busy or dirty hands.
Using the Carro Home App, create scenes to easily access pre-set fan and light settings.
Convenient Control: Hand-Held Remote 
This modern ceiling fan comes with a handy remote control that lets you turn the fan and light on/off, reverse the direction, adjust the fan speed and dim the light brightness without leaving your seat.
Press the pair button for 5 seconds to successfully connect your smart ceiling fan to the remote.
Dimmable Light Kit for Multiple Scenes 
This flush mount ceiling fan adopts 3 color temperature adjustable, and 1%-100% brightness dimmable design. DIY the lights as you like. 
For ultimate performance, the fan's light is bright and illuminating enough that you are able to change the warmth of the light in the app by changing the percentage of yellow and white light, which is nice to satisfy your need. 
Tip: The dimmable led light includes white light and yellow light. If you find the light is not completely off, that means the yellow or white light is still on. You need to turn off both l ights. 
Use Your Quiet Smart Ceiling Fan Year-Round 
This 52 inch ceiling fan is made of a whisper-quiet DC motor, saves 75% energy consumption compared to a traditional AC motor ceiling fan. 
This low profile ceiling fan with lights can downdraft in the summer and updraft in the winter, with high availability in four seasons. 
This ceiling fan with remote is built-in 10-speed wind levels, produces only about 60db noise, which barely audible and a nice breeze when you are working or sleeping. 
Fan Wattage: 26 Watts
Noise Level: ≤60Db
Number of Speed: 10
Maximum Airflow: 5090 CFM
Perfect for Indoor Spaces 
This wifi ceiling fan brings soft wind and bright light to create a comfortable environment in your baby room, study room, living room, and bedroom. 
Versatility Time Setting Performance 
Timer Function: 
This alexa ceiling fan has 1-8 hour timer settings. Set a fixed time to turn the fan off automatically, saves more energy in your daily life. 
Schedule Function: 
Enjoy a cool and bright environment by creating a schedule in advance. Set times to turn the fan, and LED lights on/off wherever you are. You can also control it individually or in groups via the app. 
Set a schedule for turning off the light at 23:00 and turning on the fan at 8:00, then you will have a sweet night and a comfortable morning in summer.

aPlusContent.title: Product Description
aPlusContent.rawText:
Product Description
52-inch Modern Voyager Smart Ceiling Fan 
This Voyager 52-inch smart ceiling fan offers a handy remote, a specialized Carro Home APP, and voice control that works with Alexa, Google Assistant, and Siri Shortcuts to adjust the fan speeds, dim the LED light, reverse fan direction, set timers and schedules. This DC motor ceiling fan is easier to install so long as the fan has an AC adapter and is capable of up to 10 levels of wind speed to enjoy a cooling summer. This black and gold ceiling fan applies multiple functions to satisfy your need and create a smart life for you. 
Chic Ceiling Fan with Dimmable LED Light 
This black ceiling fan is a simplicity designing with a black finish, using elegant plywood blades, glass shade, and a gold airfoil bracket that will bring a unique sophisticated touch to your room. Maximize the use of your ceiling fan in rooms with this smart ceiling fan.
This low profile ceiling fan with a 6-inch downrod is ETL-certified and suitable for flat or sloped surfaces (with a pitch of up to 27°). This modern ceiling fan is damp-rated that fits indoor or outdoor. (please do not pour water into the fan directly)
Chic Ceiling Fan with Dimmable LED Light 
The gold and black ceiling fan comes with 2150 lumens integrated LED kit, offers more than 50,000 hours lifespan, and produces less energy than traditional light bulbs.
This ceiling fan with light can be dimmed with brightness from 100% to 1%, and adjusted 3 color temperatures, 2700k warm light, 3500k natural light, and 4500k daylight. Easy to create the perfect lighting for any occasion:
Set the yellow light to 20% and daylight to 100% during work time.
Set the yellow light to 50% and daylight to 50% during the reading time.
Set the yellow light to 70% and daylight to 70% during family time.
High-performance DC Motor Ceiling Fan 
This 5-blades ceiling fan offers up to 10 levels of wind speed, delivers ultra-powerful airflow with a maximum of 4500 CFM, and only produces 58Db noise. To meet your need on different occasions, the gold ceiling fan was designed to have 3 different wind modes, including normal, natural, and sleep mode.
The whisper-quiet DC motor allows the ceiling fan to change the direction from downdraft mode during the summer to updraft mode during the winter, letting you have a nice and fresh environment all year round.
The high-velocity DC motor ceiling fan can save 75% energy consumption compared to a traditional AC motor ceiling fan.
3 Ways to Control Smart Ceiling Fan 
Remote control: This black ceiling fan with light comes with a handy remote control that lets you turn the fan and light on/off, reverse the direction, adjust the fan speed and dim the light brightness without leaving your seat. Press the pair button for 5 seconds to successfully connect your smart ceiling fan to the remote.
Carro Home App Control: This ceiling fan with remote can be controlled using the Carro Home App (compatible for Android and IOS devices). Easily adjust the fan speed, dim the LED lights, alternate between color temperatures, set timers, create schedules, reverse the fan direction, and change fan modes. When connecting to the app for the first time, make sure to turn off the Bluetooth and use only the 2.4Ghz network.
Voice Control: This smart ceiling fan integrates seamlessly with Alexa, Google Assistant, and Siri Shortcuts for hands-free access to your fan settings. Using a simple voice command you can control your fan speed, turn the light on/off, and even dim the brightness. Voice control is perfect in areas like your living room or kitchen where you often find yourself with busy or dirty hands. Using the Carro Home App, create scenes to easily access pre-set fan and light settings.
Timer & Schedule Function 
Timer Function: 
This indoor ceiling fan supports a timer setting that shut the fan off after 1/2/3/4/5/6/7/8 hours automatically.
Schedule Function: 
Using the modern schedule function, you can program this modern ceiling fan with dimmable LED light to meet your exact routine needs. Create a cool environment in advance or set your fan to turn off for bedtime by setting multiple schedules all from one convenient smart app.
Indoor & Outdoor Ceiling fan 
This ceiling fan is perfect for indoor or covered outdoor spaces. The fan has moisture resistance that allows the fan install outdoor like on patios, porches, and garages. Stylish design make the reversible ceiling fan suitable for living room, bedroom, kitchen, baby room, and study room.

Product Description
10-speed, 3-Blade Smart Ceiling Fan with LED Light Kit & REMOTE - Light Wooden Pattern 
· This Striver 52'' smart ceiling fan keeps your space cool, bright, and stylish. It is a soft modern masterpiece perfect for your large indoor living spaces. This Wifi smart ceiling fan is a simplicity designing with White finish, use very strong ABS blades(color likes light wooden pattern) and has an integrated 4000K LED daylight. The fan features Remote control, Wi-Fi apps and Voice control technology (compatible with Amazon Alexa and Google Home Assistant, but not included) to set fan preferences. 
·Notice: SMAAIR Striver Smart Ceiling Fan Series need to be flush-mounted installation and cannot be angled. 
Dimmable Light Kit for Multiple Scenes 
· The integrated LED light kit produces warm soft white and bright cool white. With 1800 lumens super bright LED kit, you can choose the color temperature 2700K to 4000K according to your needs. 
· On any occasion, you could change the lighting color and brightness as you like. For example, it will make sure your eyes get better protection through adjusting the light when your eyes tired. 
Versatility Time Setting Performance 
· Timer Setting: Ceiling fan offers multiple speed settings, timing function of 1-8 hour, different mounting options, and a quiet motor while relaxing and enjoying. 
· Schedule Setting: This low profile ceiling fan offers a schedule setting function of controlling the fan turn on/off, yellow light or white light on/off at any time away from home. You can also control it individually or group.

1. Why does my fan stop working suddenly? I press the buttom and it has no responce. 
The fan will be auto off when the fan is blocked from working in 3rd speed. It can work normally after charging it.If the action mentioned above don't work, please contcact us on Amazon, and we will reply you within 24 hours. 
2..Why didn't I receive the battery? Do I need buy an extra battery? 
The rechargeable battery is in the fan so you don't need to buy another battery or load the battery. Just use it and charge it when its battery runs out of power. 
3. How long does the battery take to charge a full charge? 
When charging the battery, there is a red light, it will becomes to green light if the battery is fully recharged. The charging time is about 3 hours, please make sure it's fully charged before shutting off power. 
4. What kind of the charging cable does the fan use? How to recharge the mini handheld fan? 
We optimize die structure of the fan. It use USB-C cable since 2023 and before that it use USB-B cable . 
Connect the inlcuded USB cable to 5V output adapter like phone charger, or power bank, or other USB outlet devices to charge the fan. 
5. Can I use it on a stroller? 
Yes. it comes with a metal clip, please find the two holes in the sides above the handle, insert the clip along the two grooves, so that it can be used in a stroller, office folding screen, pram, camping tent, student's bed, etc.
